1
00:00:02,294 --> 00:00:04,262
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Palmer figured out that we're
doing this with Seidel.</b></i></font>

2
00:00:04,338 --> 00:00:05,840
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And unless
we drop the lawsuit,</b></i></font>

3
00:00:05,923 --> 00:00:07,175
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>he's going to come
after us for collusion.</b></i></font>

4
00:00:07,257 --> 00:00:09,351
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If I pull out of that hearing,
Palmer can't touch us.</b></i></font>

5
00:00:09,426 --> 00:00:12,145
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'm not doing anything until you
tell Nathan exactly what's going on.</b></i></font>

6
00:00:12,221 --> 00:00:13,313
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's nothing to tell.</b></i></font>

7
00:00:13,388 --> 00:00:15,482
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You said you were doing this case
as a way to get into the Bar.</b></i></font>

8
00:00:15,557 --> 00:00:17,025
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I just
withdrew my application.</b></i></font>

9
00:00:17,100 --> 00:00:19,148
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I knew Mike was a fraud
before he was arrested.</b></i></font>

10
00:00:19,228 --> 00:00:21,071
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I leveraged it to get
my name on the wall.</b></i></font>

11
00:00:21,146 --> 00:00:22,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I thought I knew
what kind of man you were.</b></i></font>

12
00:00:22,856 --> 00:00:24,153
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How dare you say
that to me?</b></i></font>

13
00:00:24,233 --> 00:00:26,907
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The first time we slept together,
you were with another man.</b></i></font>

14
00:00:26,985 --> 00:00:28,658
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't want to spend
the rest of my life</b></i></font>

15
00:00:28,737 --> 00:00:30,330
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>with a man who gave up
on his dreams.</b></i></font>

16
00:00:30,405 --> 00:00:32,828
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I know that you don't
want to be that man either.</b></i></font>

17
00:00:32,908 --> 00:00:35,002
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We have proof
of over a dozen instances</b></i></font>

18
00:00:35,077 --> 00:00:36,557
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>of you committing
corporate espionage.</b></i></font>

19
00:00:36,578 --> 00:00:37,704
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you want?</b></i></font>

20
00:00:37,788 --> 00:00:38,880
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're going to
settle with those miners.</b></i></font>

21
00:00:38,956 --> 00:00:40,253
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're going to forget
you ever heard of us.</b></i></font>

22
00:00:40,332 --> 00:00:43,051
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you're going to honor your
original agreement with Craig Seidel.</b></i></font>

23
00:00:43,126 --> 00:00:44,378
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't just want you
to set that hearing.</b></i></font>

24
00:00:44,461 --> 00:00:47,135
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want you to bulldoze
anyone who stands in my way.</b></i></font>

25
00:00:55,806 --> 00:00:57,183
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What time is it?</b></i></font>

26
00:00:57,891 --> 00:01:00,770
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Don't worry. You're
not late for work.</b></i></font>

27
00:01:01,812 --> 00:01:02,938
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Here.</b></i></font>

28
00:01:03,021 --> 00:01:04,193
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thanks.</b></i></font>

29
00:01:04,273 --> 00:01:06,071
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>God, I could use this.</b></i></font>

30
00:01:06,149 --> 00:01:07,617
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I got in pretty late
last night.</b></i></font>

31
00:01:07,693 --> 00:01:10,572
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Does that have anything
to do with the flowers</b></i></font>

32
00:01:10,654 --> 00:01:12,201
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just found
in the kitchen?</b></i></font>

33
00:01:13,448 --> 00:01:15,371
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Can't a guy just buy you
flowers because he loves you?</b></i></font>

34
00:01:15,450 --> 00:01:16,450
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He can.</b></i></font>

35
00:01:16,493 --> 00:01:17,995
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But he didn't.</b></i></font>

36
00:01:19,162 --> 00:01:20,630
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're right.</b></i></font>

37
00:01:21,665 --> 00:01:23,417
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I bought them</b></i></font>

38
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:25,377
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to say thank you
for doing whatever it took</b></i></font>

39
00:01:25,460 --> 00:01:28,304
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to make sure I got my shot
at getting into the Bar.</b></i></font>

40
00:01:28,422 --> 00:01:30,049
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Wait, does that mean that...
Yeah.</b></i></font>

41
00:01:30,132 --> 00:01:31,258
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We did it.</b></i></font>

42
00:01:31,341 --> 00:01:33,184
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>My hearing's tomorrow.</b></i></font>

43
00:01:33,635 --> 00:01:35,182
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Seidel's on our side.</b></i></font>

44
00:01:36,096 --> 00:01:37,848
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I can't believe it.</b></i></font>

45
00:01:38,515 --> 00:01:40,017
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This could
really happen.</b></i></font>

46
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:41,317
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know.</b></i></font>

47
00:01:43,395 --> 00:01:44,487
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What is it?</b></i></font>

48
00:01:44,563 --> 00:01:47,658
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I promised Oliver that I would
tell Nathan about the whole thing.</b></i></font>

49
00:01:47,774 --> 00:01:50,027
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, you can't do that.
I know I can't.</b></i></font>

50
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:52,321
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I've got to get a couple
of days off for the hearing.</b></i></font>

51
00:01:52,404 --> 00:01:55,328
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which means I've got
to tell him something.</b></i></font>

52
00:02:04,458 --> 00:02:07,428
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis. What are
you doing here?</b></i></font>

53
00:02:07,502 --> 00:02:09,004
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I hope you don't mind
I stopped by.</b></i></font>

54
00:02:09,087 --> 00:02:12,261
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I had to see you. I couldn't
sleep at all last night.</b></i></font>

55
00:02:12,341 --> 00:02:13,341
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Neither could I.</b></i></font>

56
00:02:13,383 --> 00:02:15,977
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tara, please.
I know we had a fight.</b></i></font>

57
00:02:16,053 --> 00:02:18,397
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But you told me you
wanted to get to know me.</b></i></font>

58
00:02:18,472 --> 00:02:22,272
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I swear, what I told you was
the worst thing I've ever done.</b></i></font>

59
00:02:22,351 --> 00:02:24,024
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, the thing I'm having
trouble dealing with</b></i></font>

60
00:02:24,102 --> 00:02:26,776
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>has nothing to do with
that person at your firm.</b></i></font>

61
00:02:26,855 --> 00:02:28,653
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It has to do with how you
treated me last night.</b></i></font>

62
00:02:28,732 --> 00:02:30,325
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tara, please.
Let me finish.</b></i></font>

63
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,993
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You shared something
horrible with me,</b></i></font>

64
00:02:32,069 --> 00:02:33,992
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>gave me no time
to process it</b></i></font>

65
00:02:34,071 --> 00:02:35,994
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and while
I was taking it in,</b></i></font>

66
00:02:36,073 --> 00:02:38,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you not only attacked
my integrity,</b></i></font>

67
00:02:38,909 --> 00:02:40,832
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you made me feel
ashamed of myself.</b></i></font>

68
00:02:40,911 --> 00:02:43,960
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You are right. I lashed
out and I shouldn't have.</b></i></font>

69
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:46,918
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I only did it because I was
afraid of you rejecting me.</b></i></font>

70
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,798
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I will...</b></i></font>

71
00:02:48,877 --> 00:02:51,050
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tara, I will die
if you reject me.</b></i></font>

72
00:02:51,129 --> 00:02:53,052
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's the thing,
Louis.</b></i></font>

73
00:02:53,131 --> 00:02:56,431
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You had a reason for
reacting the way you did.</b></i></font>

74
00:02:58,762 --> 00:03:01,185
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'm not sure
I want to be with a man</b></i></font>

75
00:03:01,264 --> 00:03:03,483
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>who thinks there's ever a
reason to treat me that way.</b></i></font>

76
00:03:03,558 --> 00:03:04,935
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tara.
I'm sorry, Louis.</b></i></font>

77
00:03:05,018 --> 00:03:06,565
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They're waiting for me
in the conference room.</b></i></font>

78
00:03:06,645 --> 00:03:10,741
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I told you I'll call,
and I will call.</b></i></font>

79
00:03:21,076 --> 00:03:22,168
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Nathan.</b></i></font>

80
00:03:22,244 --> 00:03:23,245
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, what's up?</b></i></font>

81
00:03:23,328 --> 00:03:25,956
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Nothing. I just want
to give you this.</b></i></font>

82
00:03:28,291 --> 00:03:29,918
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This is a check
for $50,000.</b></i></font>

83
00:03:30,001 --> 00:03:31,298
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know.
We settled.</b></i></font>

84
00:03:31,378 --> 00:03:33,051
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I gave the miners
their checks last night.</b></i></font>

85
00:03:33,130 --> 00:03:35,730
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, this is the most
money we've ever made on a case.</b></i></font>

86
00:03:35,757 --> 00:03:37,555
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>For once, we're not going to
have to worry about making rent.</b></i></font>

87
00:03:37,634 --> 00:03:39,352
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, right.</b></i></font>

88
00:03:39,428 --> 00:03:40,680
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's not a joke.</b></i></font>

89
00:03:40,762 --> 00:03:42,480
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Wait, you're telling me
that $50,000</b></i></font>

90
00:03:42,556 --> 00:03:44,058
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>can really make that big a
difference to the clinic?</b></i></font>

91
00:03:44,141 --> 00:03:45,563
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm telling you that I
know, in corporate law,</b></i></font>

92
00:03:45,642 --> 00:03:48,065
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>money doesn't matter
unless it's in the millions.</b></i></font>

93
00:03:48,145 --> 00:03:50,648
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But here, $50,000 makes all
the difference in the world.</b></i></font>

94
00:03:51,106 --> 00:03:52,858
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, in that case, Nathan,</b></i></font>

95
00:03:52,941 --> 00:03:55,239
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've been working here seven
days a week since I started</b></i></font>

96
00:03:55,318 --> 00:03:57,241
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I've got some personal stuff
that I need to take care of...</b></i></font>

97
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,367
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Stop right there.</b></i></font>

98
00:03:58,447 --> 00:03:59,573
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Look. You just bought me
30 days' rent.</b></i></font>

99
00:03:59,656 --> 00:04:01,336
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The least I can do
is give a few days back.</b></i></font>

100
00:04:02,409 --> 00:04:03,410
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Right.</b></i></font>

101
00:04:03,493 --> 00:04:04,710
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you.
Thank you.</b></i></font>

102
00:04:14,463 --> 00:04:15,555
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay,
let's hear it.</b></i></font>

103
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:16,630
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Hear what?</b></i></font>

104
00:04:16,673 --> 00:04:18,175
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The joke you spent
all morning coming up with.</b></i></font>

105
00:04:18,258 --> 00:04:19,259
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What joke?</b></i></font>

106
00:04:19,342 --> 00:04:20,764
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I was just going to ask you
where the law library was,</b></i></font>

107
00:04:20,844 --> 00:04:22,562
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but then I realized you've
never set foot in there.</b></i></font>

108
00:04:22,637 --> 00:04:24,605
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Shouldn't you be at the
clinic saving whales?</b></i></font>

109
00:04:24,681 --> 00:04:25,728
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>First of all,
that's Greenpeace.</b></i></font>

110
00:04:25,807 --> 00:04:27,150
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And second of all,</b></i></font>

111
00:04:27,225 --> 00:04:28,665
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I took the day off
so I could prepare</b></i></font>

112
00:04:28,685 --> 00:04:29,982
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>for the character
and fitness committee.</b></i></font>

113
00:04:30,061 --> 00:04:31,141
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh! That means
you're taking</b></i></font>

114
00:04:31,188 --> 00:04:32,656
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>whatever that hitch is
going to be seriously.</b></i></font>

115
00:04:32,731 --> 00:04:33,778
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You know I am.</b></i></font>

116
00:04:33,857 --> 00:04:34,949
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's what
I like to hear,</b></i></font>

117
00:04:35,025 --> 00:04:36,777
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because I don't want
somebody working here</b></i></font>

118
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:38,203
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>who doesn't listen
to my advice.</b></i></font>

119
00:04:38,862 --> 00:04:40,660
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I still don't
think you understand.</b></i></font>

120
00:04:40,739 --> 00:04:42,867
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>When this thing is over,
I am not coming back here.</b></i></font>

121
00:04:42,949 --> 00:04:43,950
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike.
I told you.</b></i></font>

122
00:04:44,034 --> 00:04:45,126
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want to do good.</b></i></font>

123
00:04:45,202 --> 00:04:46,294
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then do good here.</b></i></font>

124
00:04:46,369 --> 00:04:47,712
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I also told you
that the only reason</b></i></font>

125
00:04:47,788 --> 00:04:49,665
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I agreed to this whole
thing in the first place</b></i></font>

126
00:04:49,748 --> 00:04:51,967
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>was because I couldn't stand to
watch someone like Oliver fail</b></i></font>

127
00:04:52,042 --> 00:04:53,294
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and not be able
to help him.</b></i></font>

128
00:04:53,376 --> 00:04:55,496
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And people like Oliver don't
work in places like this,</b></i></font>

129
00:04:55,504 --> 00:04:56,972
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>they work
in places like that.</b></i></font>

130
00:04:57,047 --> 00:04:59,596
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And people like you shouldn't
be working anywhere.</b></i></font>

131
00:04:59,674 --> 00:05:01,267
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you
doing here, Anita?</b></i></font>

132
00:05:01,343 --> 00:05:02,970
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm here because
the US Attorney's office</b></i></font>

133
00:05:03,053 --> 00:05:06,273
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>requested that they be notified if
Mike Ross ever applied to the Bar.</b></i></font>

134
00:05:06,348 --> 00:05:08,567
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What does the US Attorney's
office have to do with Mike?</b></i></font>

135
00:05:08,642 --> 00:05:09,768
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Nothing.</b></i></font>

136
00:05:09,851 --> 00:05:11,444
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Except I happen
to work there.</b></i></font>

137
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,817
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And as of one week ago,</b></i></font>

138
00:05:12,896 --> 00:05:15,319
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm also the newest member of the
character and fitness committee.</b></i></font>

139
00:05:15,398 --> 00:05:16,399
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bullshit.</b></i></font>

140
00:05:16,483 --> 00:05:17,951
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's a whole process
to get on that committee.</b></i></font>

141
00:05:18,026 --> 00:05:20,028
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's no way you just
happened to be in the pipeline.</b></i></font>

142
00:05:20,111 --> 00:05:21,408
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're right.
I wasn't.</b></i></font>

143
00:05:21,488 --> 00:05:22,990
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But when a member
takes leave,</b></i></font>

144
00:05:23,073 --> 00:05:25,417
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>he has the right
to appoint his replacement.</b></i></font>

145
00:05:25,492 --> 00:05:27,836
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And Walter Samson
appointed me.</b></i></font>

146
00:05:27,911 --> 00:05:29,591
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You think
I'm not going to find out</b></i></font>

147
00:05:29,621 --> 00:05:31,294
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>whatever bullshit you did
to get this guy to drop out?</b></i></font>

148
00:05:31,373 --> 00:05:32,374
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Be my guest.</b></i></font>

149
00:05:32,457 --> 00:05:34,300
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because if Mike is going
before that hearing,</b></i></font>

150
00:05:34,376 --> 00:05:36,128
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that means you did
something, too.</b></i></font>

151
00:05:36,503 --> 00:05:37,504
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you want?</b></i></font>

152
00:05:37,587 --> 00:05:38,588
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want to tell you</b></i></font>

153
00:05:38,672 --> 00:05:40,174
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you might as well
cancel this hearing</b></i></font>

154
00:05:40,257 --> 00:05:41,850
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and save us all
a lot of time.</b></i></font>

155
00:05:41,925 --> 00:05:43,723
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because the vote
has to be unanimous.</b></i></font>

156
00:05:43,802 --> 00:05:47,022
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you are never
getting my vote.</b></i></font>

157
00:05:51,935 --> 00:05:55,189
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>See the money,
wanna stay for your meal</b></i></font>

158
00:05:55,272 --> 00:05:58,617
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Get another piece of pie
for your wife</b></i></font>

159
00:05:58,692 --> 00:06:01,821
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Everybody wanna know
how it feel</b></i></font>

160
00:06:01,903 --> 00:06:05,282
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Everybody wanna see
what it's like</b></i></font>

161
00:06:05,365 --> 00:06:08,460
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'll even eat a bean pie
I don't mind</b></i></font>

162
00:06:08,535 --> 00:06:10,378
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Me and missy is so early</b></i></font>

163
00:06:10,453 --> 00:06:12,171
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Busy, busy making money</b></i></font>

