<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why should I believe
the word of a liar?</b></i></font>

327
00:12:04,057 --> 00:12:06,435
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because of what I did for
those miners and the clinic.</b></i></font>

328
00:12:06,517 --> 00:12:08,815
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if that's not enough, how
about what I did for you?</b></i></font>

329
00:12:08,895 --> 00:12:10,112
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You didn't do
shit for me.</b></i></font>

330
00:12:10,563 --> 00:12:12,486
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But fine,
I won't tell Nathan.</b></i></font>

331
00:12:12,565 --> 00:12:14,085
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Just so long as
when this thing's over,</b></i></font>

332
00:12:14,108 --> 00:12:15,735
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you go back to your
corrupt corporate world.</b></i></font>

333
00:12:15,818 --> 00:12:18,287
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I don't care
what you tell yourself,</b></i></font>

334
00:12:18,363 --> 00:12:19,865
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you're never going
to belong in mine.</b></i></font>

335
00:12:31,668 --> 00:12:33,511
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, what are you
still doing here?</b></i></font>

336
00:12:33,586 --> 00:12:35,146
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The hearing's across town
in 10 minutes.</b></i></font>

337
00:12:35,171 --> 00:12:37,094
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not going to the hearing,
Donna, and neither are you.</b></i></font>

338
00:12:37,173 --> 00:12:38,299
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why not?</b></i></font>

339
00:12:38,383 --> 00:12:40,226
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because if you and I
can't do what we need to,</b></i></font>

340
00:12:40,301 --> 00:12:42,554
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>whatever Mike does at that
hearing isn't going to matter.</b></i></font>

341
00:12:42,637 --> 00:12:43,763
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Give it to me.</b></i></font>

342
00:12:43,846 --> 00:12:45,598
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We need to figure out what
Walter Samson's weak spot is.</b></i></font>

343
00:12:45,682 --> 00:12:47,059
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tell me how
and I'm all in.</b></i></font>

344
00:12:47,141 --> 00:12:49,360
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Start by contacting
every person we know</b></i></font>

345
00:12:49,435 --> 00:12:50,937
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and asking them what they
know about this asshole.</b></i></font>

346
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:52,943
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because Gibbs has
something on him.</b></i></font>

347
00:12:53,022 --> 00:12:57,619
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if I can't find out what it is, then
I can't get her off that committee.</b></i></font>

348
00:12:57,860 --> 00:12:58,952
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Where are you going?</b></i></font>

349
00:12:59,028 --> 00:13:01,326
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>To see someone who doesn't
know Samson at all.</b></i></font>

350
00:13:03,533 --> 00:13:04,534
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Before we get started,</b></i></font>

351
00:13:04,617 --> 00:13:07,120
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'd like to point out these
interviews are normally for us</b></i></font>

352
00:13:07,203 --> 00:13:09,547
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to quickly approve standard
applicants to the Bar.</b></i></font>

353
00:13:09,622 --> 00:13:11,920
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>However, Mr. Ross is
no standard applicant.</b></i></font>

354
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:14,298
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Therefore, we will convene
for as long as it takes</b></i></font>

355
00:13:14,377 --> 00:13:16,971
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>before ruling
on his application.</b></i></font>

356
00:13:17,046 --> 00:13:18,046
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now...</b></i></font>

357
00:13:18,089 --> 00:13:19,306
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mr. Chairman, if I may.</b></i></font>

358
00:13:19,382 --> 00:13:21,976
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Last winter,
Mr. Ross pled guilty</b></i></font>

359
00:13:22,051 --> 00:13:23,849
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to defrauding
the citizens of New York.</b></i></font>

360
00:13:23,928 --> 00:13:27,148
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Therefore, I propose we reject
his application right now,</b></i></font>

361
00:13:27,223 --> 00:13:31,319
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because Mr. Ross is a felon and the
New York Bar does not accept felons.</b></i></font>

362
00:13:31,394 --> 00:13:32,816
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mr. Chairman,
with all due respect</b></i></font>

363
00:13:32,895 --> 00:13:34,647
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to the new board member,
you do.</b></i></font>

364
00:13:34,731 --> 00:13:36,654
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Not only does
the Bar accept felons,</b></i></font>

365
00:13:36,733 --> 00:13:40,408
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but years ago, this very
committee admitted Neal Wiesner,</b></i></font>

366
00:13:40,486 --> 00:13:43,410
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>a man who spent years in
prison for attempted murder.</b></i></font>

367
00:13:43,489 --> 00:13:46,163
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now, Ms. Gibbs may think my crime
is worse than attempted murder,</b></i></font>

368
00:13:46,242 --> 00:13:48,995
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I don't think it's worth
throwing away 140 years of precedent</b></i></font>

369
00:13:49,078 --> 00:13:51,172
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>by not even allowing me
to make my case.</b></i></font>

370
00:13:57,086 --> 00:13:59,839
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Come on, let's go.
Come on.</b></i></font>

371
00:13:59,922 --> 00:14:01,765
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Come on. Shit.</b></i></font>

372
00:14:02,717 --> 00:14:04,094
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What the hell
are you doing?</b></i></font>

373
00:14:04,218 --> 00:14:05,344
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What does it look
like I'm doing?</b></i></font>

374
00:14:05,428 --> 00:14:06,725
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm watching my money
go down the toilet.</b></i></font>

375
00:14:06,804 --> 00:14:09,353
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, it looks to me
like I paid you to do a job</b></i></font>

376
00:14:09,432 --> 00:14:11,150
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and you're sitting here
doing this.</b></i></font>

377
00:14:11,225 --> 00:14:12,693
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay, I'll let you in
on a little secret.</b></i></font>

378
00:14:12,769 --> 00:14:15,363
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It only takes 15 minutes
to hack someone.</b></i></font>

379
00:14:15,438 --> 00:14:17,156
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you can't find something
in the next 45,</b></i></font>

380
00:14:17,231 --> 00:14:18,403
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>it means there's
nothing to find.</b></i></font>

381
00:14:18,483 --> 00:14:20,163
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bullshit. There's always
something to find.</b></i></font>

382
00:14:20,234 --> 00:14:21,781
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm telling you
there isn't.</b></i></font>

383
00:14:21,861 --> 00:14:23,909
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He doesn't drink, smoke,
gamble, cheat, nothing.</b></i></font>

384
00:14:23,988 --> 00:14:25,035
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Listen to me.</b></i></font>

385
00:14:25,114 --> 00:14:26,832
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I paid you good
money to do a job,</b></i></font>

386
00:14:26,908 --> 00:14:28,581
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and if you don't put some
more effort into this,</b></i></font>

387
00:14:28,659 --> 00:14:30,859
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm going to spread the word
that you aren't worth shit.</b></i></font>

388
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:32,872
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And this time, it won't be
coming from Louis Litt.</b></i></font>

389
00:14:32,955 --> 00:14:34,172
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It will be coming
from me.</b></i></font>

390
00:14:34,248 --> 00:14:35,248
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then keep
your damn money.</b></i></font>

391
00:14:35,291 --> 00:14:38,010
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>When I tell you there's nothing
to find, there's nothing to find.</b></i></font>

392
00:14:40,004 --> 00:14:41,677
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I guess
what I'm saying is,</b></i></font>

393
00:14:41,756 --> 00:14:45,511
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>not only do I admit
what I did,</b></i></font>

394
00:14:45,593 --> 00:14:50,394
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I regret it with
every fiber of my being,</b></i></font>

395
00:14:51,265 --> 00:14:55,691
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I'd like to apologize to my
clients, my former colleagues,</b></i></font>

396
00:14:55,770 --> 00:14:58,114
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and finally, to the
fraternity of men and women</b></i></font>

397
00:14:58,189 --> 00:15:01,614
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that I have wanted to be a
member of since I was a child.</b></i></font>

398
00:15:06,155 --> 00:15:07,657
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, that was
a moving statement.</b></i></font>

399
00:15:07,740 --> 00:15:09,242
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just have one question.</b></i></font>

400
00:15:09,325 --> 00:15:10,998
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you regret
what you did so much,</b></i></font>

401
00:15:11,077 --> 00:15:13,125
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>why weren't you willing
to serve your full sentence?</b></i></font>

402
00:15:13,204 --> 00:15:14,501
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I wasn't unwilling.</b></i></font>

403
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:16,423
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I was offered a deal
to help convict</b></i></font>

404
00:15:16,499 --> 00:15:18,251
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>a known criminal
and I took it.</b></i></font>

405
00:15:18,334 --> 00:15:20,757
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You were offered a deal to get
out early and you took it.</b></i></font>

406
00:15:20,837 --> 00:15:22,510
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I protected
an innocent man and...</b></i></font>

407
00:15:22,588 --> 00:15:25,341
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What you did was insinuate yourself
into your roommate's life,</b></i></font>

408
00:15:25,425 --> 00:15:27,302
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>gain his trust, and
pretend to be his friend.</b></i></font>

409
00:15:27,385 --> 00:15:28,887
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>True or false?</b></i></font>

410
00:15:31,180 --> 00:15:32,477
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're taking it
out of context.</b></i></font>

411
00:15:32,557 --> 00:15:34,184
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The context is
you portrayed yourself</b></i></font>

412
00:15:34,267 --> 00:15:36,110
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>as one thing, when really,
you were another,</b></i></font>

413
00:15:36,185 --> 00:15:39,234
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>which is what you did the entire time
you pretended to be an attorney,</b></i></font>

414
00:15:39,313 --> 00:15:42,032
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and what I believe you are
doing to this body right now.</b></i></font>

415
00:15:43,192 --> 00:15:47,413
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mr. Chairman, if she's going to impugn
his character while he's speaking,</b></i></font>

416
00:15:47,488 --> 00:15:49,582
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>then he's entitled to let
someone else speak for him.</b></i></font>

417
00:15:49,657 --> 00:15:50,704
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This
isn't a trial.</b></i></font>

418
00:15:50,783 --> 00:15:52,456
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We don't allow
character witnesses here.</b></i></font>

419
00:15:52,535 --> 00:15:53,627
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Actually, you do.</b></i></font>

420
00:15:53,703 --> 00:15:55,580
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Article IV, 16A.</b></i></font>

421
00:15:55,663 --> 00:15:57,461
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Applicants are
allowed a witness</b></i></font>

422
00:15:57,540 --> 00:15:59,008
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>as a rebuttal
for an accusation</b></i></font>

423
00:15:59,083 --> 00:16:00,801
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>leveled by
a committee member.</b></i></font>

424
00:16:00,877 --> 00:16:03,255
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That article hasn't
been cited in 30 years.</b></i></font>

425
00:16:03,337 --> 00:16:04,964
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Maybe that's because
no applicant</b></i></font>

426
00:16:05,047 --> 00:16:06,567
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>has ever had to stand
before the person</b></i></font>

427
00:16:06,632 --> 00:16:07,724
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>who put them away.</b></i></font>

428
00:16:07,925 --> 00:16:09,142
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You make a point.</b></i></font>

429
00:16:09,218 --> 00:16:11,738
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We'll pick this up first thing in
the morning with your witness.</b></i></font>

430
00:16:11,762 --> 00:16:13,105
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you.</b></i></font>

431
00:16:17,768 --> 00:16:19,862
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, that was
exactly what I needed.</b></i></font>

432
00:16:19,937 --> 00:16:21,154
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you hadn't done that...
I know.</b></i></font>

433
00:16:21,230 --> 00:16:22,356
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But right now, I'm more
concerned with the fact</b></i></font>

434
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,987
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that she's turning
them against you.</b></i></font>

435
00:16:24,066 --> 00:16:26,990
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which means even after
Harvey kicks her off,</b></i></font>

436
00:16:27,069 --> 00:16:29,538
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Seidel's job is going
to be that much harder.</b></i></font>

437
00:16:29,906 --> 00:16:32,455
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And we only have one shot at
having someone speak for me.</b></i></font>

438
00:16:32,533 --> 00:16:33,625
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, come on.</b></i></font>

439
00:16:33,701 --> 00:16:34,873
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We've got to get back
to the office</b></i></font>

440
00:16:34,952 --> 00:16:36,712
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and start going through
everyone it could be.</b></i></font>

441
00:16:36,787 --> 00:16:38,881
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We'll make a list of pros
and cons and... Rachel.</b></i></font>

442
00:16:39,749 --> 00:16:41,547
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know who it is.</b></i></font>

443
00:16:51,344 --> 00:16:52,561
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Julius.</b></i></font>

444
00:16:54,222 --> 00:16:55,314
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike.</b></i></font>

445
00:16:56,140 --> 00:16:57,141
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you doing here?</b></i></font>

446
00:16:57,225 --> 00:16:58,818
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I was hoping
that we could talk.</b></i></font>

447
00:16:58,893 --> 00:17:01,521
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Look, I'm sorry, man.
This is not a good time.</b></i></font>

448
00:17:01,604 --> 00:17:03,277
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just put the baby down
and the wife and I...</b></i></font>

449
00:17:03,356 --> 00:17:04,858
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Please, it won't
take long.</b></i></font>

450
00:17:04,941 --> 00:17:06,113
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've got this
hearing tomorrow</b></i></font>

451
00:17:06,192 --> 00:17:08,536
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>for the character portion
of the Bar.</b></i></font>

452
00:17:08,611 --> 00:17:10,363
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I wanted to ask
if you'd speak for me.</b></i></font>

453
00:17:11,364 --> 00:17:13,332
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You mind if I ask, why me?</b></i></font>

454
00:17:13,407 --> 00:17:14,408
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because you're
the only one I know</b></i></font>

455
00:17:14,492 --> 00:17:15,584
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>who's qualified
to tell the board</b></i></font>

456
00:17:15,660 --> 00:17:18,413
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that I was a different man when
I got out than when I went in.</b></i></font>

457
00:17:19,664 --> 00:17:21,587
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No offense, Mike.</b></i></font>

458
00:17:21,666 --> 00:17:24,215
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But the truth is
I'm not sure you are.</b></i></font>

459
00:17:24,293 --> 00:17:25,293
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean?</b></i></font>

460
00:17:25,336 --> 00:17:27,009
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I mean you said this
hearing is tomorrow,</b></i></font>

461
00:17:27,088 --> 00:17:28,385
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but you're just now
coming to me.</b></i></font>

462
00:17:28,464 --> 00:17:30,432
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which means
something's going on.</b></i></font>

463
00:17:30,508 --> 00:17:32,228
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's going on is the
woman who put me away</b></i></font>

464
00:17:32,301 --> 00:17:33,861
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>managed to get herself
on the committee,</b></i></font>

465
00:17:33,928 --> 00:17:35,305
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and now she's slamming
the door in my face.</b></i></font>

466
00:17:35,388 --> 00:17:36,428
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And why would she do that?</b></i></font>

467
00:17:36,472 --> 00:17:37,473
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Julius, I'm not...</b></i></font>

468
00:17:37,557 --> 00:17:38,774
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, how did you
even get a hearing?</b></i></font>

469
00:17:38,849 --> 00:17:39,975
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you
talking about?</b></i></font>

470
00:17:40,059 --> 00:17:41,231
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I applied
like everyone else.</b></i></font>

471
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:43,187
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No. You're not
like everyone else.</b></i></font>

472
00:17:43,271 --> 00:17:44,351
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You didn't go
to law school.</b></i></font>

473
00:17:44,397 --> 00:17:46,650
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It doesn't matter. There's an
exception called Reading the Law.</b></i></font>

474
00:17:46,732 --> 00:17:47,772
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You see?
Right there, Mike.</b></i></font>

475
00:17:47,817 --> 00:17:50,286
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That sounds like the bullshit
artist I met in prison.</b></i></font>

476
00:17:50,361 --> 00:17:51,908
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So you tell me right now.</b></i></font>

477
00:17:51,988 --> 00:17:53,911
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Did you pull some shit
to make this happen?</b></i></font>

478
00:17:55,783 --> 00:17:56,783
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Damn, Mike.</b></i></font>

479
00:17:56,826 --> 00:17:57,998
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you can't be
straight with me,</b></i></font>

480
00:17:58,077 --> 00:18:00,205
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>this conversation
ends right here.</b></i></font>

481
00:18:00,871 --> 00:18:01,963
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yes. I did.</b></i></font>

482
00:18:03,708 --> 00:18:04,755
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Ah...</b></i></font>

483
00:18:04,959 --> 00:18:07,337
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Finally,
some truth in the night.</b></i></font>

484
00:18:08,337 --> 00:18:11,557
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Julius, I work at a law
clinic, but not as a lawyer.</b></i></font>

485
00:18:11,632 --> 00:18:13,305
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>An opportunity
presented itself for me</b></i></font>

486
00:18:13,384 --> 00:18:14,636
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to become one
and I turned it down.</b></i></font>

487
00:18:14,719 --> 00:18:16,813
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But then, I had to sit
there and watch a woman</b></i></font>

488
00:18:16,887 --> 00:18:17,979
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>get put on the street</b></i></font>

489
00:18:18,055 --> 00:18:19,227
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because I couldn't
help her.</b></i></font>

490
00:18:19,807 --> 00:18:21,400
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I knew that I'd have
to watch that happen</b></i></font>

491
00:18:21,475 --> 00:18:23,022
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>over and over
and over.</b></i></font>

492
00:18:23,102 --> 00:18:27,278
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, when that opportunity presented
itself for the second time, I took it.</b></i></font>

493
00:18:27,356 --> 00:18:28,824
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I knew it would
never come along again.</b></i></font>

494
00:18:28,858 --> 00:18:30,610
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't know that, Mike.
I do know that.</b></i></font>

495
00:18:30,693 --> 00:18:32,616
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So you can say no
if you want to,</b></i></font>

496
00:18:32,695 --> 00:18:34,743
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but don't say
I haven't changed.</b></i></font>

497
00:18:34,822 --> 00:18:36,495
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because the Mike you met
that night in prison</b></i></font>

498
00:18:36,574 --> 00:18:38,997
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>never would have told you
the truth just now.</b></i></font>

499
00:18:41,787 --> 00:18:43,414
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Julius, please.</b></i></font>

500
00:18:47,418 --> 00:18:48,840
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need this.</b></i></font>

501
00:18:52,882 --> 00:18:56,056
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This is the address.
It's tomorrow at 9:00.</b></i></font>

502
00:18:59,639 --> 00:19:01,641
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't have anyone else.</b></i></font>

503
00:19:17,406 --> 00:19:18,623
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, hey.</b></i></font>

504
00:19:18,699 --> 00:19:20,579
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, tell me
you've got some good news.</b></i></font>

505
00:19:21,035 --> 00:19:23,333
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I do.
I took care of Seidel.</b></i></font>

506
00:19:23,412 --> 00:19:24,532
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He's still going
to back you.</b></i></font>

507
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:25,832
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not talking
about Seidel.</b></i></font>

508
00:19:25,915 --> 00:19:27,917
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm talking about getting
Gibbs off that committee.</b></i></font>

509
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,047
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's not that simple.</b></i></font>

510
00:19:29,126 --> 00:19:30,753
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's not that
simple about it?</b></i></font>

511
00:19:31,545 --> 00:19:33,513
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I haven't found
anything on him yet.</b></i></font>

512
00:19:33,589 --> 00:19:35,967
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I am struggling
to get someone on my side.</b></i></font>

513
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:37,890
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And every second
that she is on that committee,</b></i></font>

514
00:19:37,927 --> 00:19:40,521
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>she is turning
people against me.</b></i></font>

515
00:19:40,596 --> 00:19:41,939
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need your help.</b></i></font>

516
00:19:42,014 --> 00:19:43,106
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike.</b></i></font>

517
00:19:43,516 --> 00:19:47,271
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I told you I'd get it done.
I'll get it done.</b></i></font>

518
00:19:50,773 --> 00:19:52,446
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Anything?
No.</b></i></font>

519
00:19:52,525 --> 00:19:54,118
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's the same as when
you called an hour ago.</b></i></font>

520
00:19:54,193 --> 00:19:56,537
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If he killed somebody and hid the
body, nobody knows where it is.</b></i></font>

521
00:19:56,612 --> 00:19:58,205
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then why don't you tell me
who's next on the list?</b></i></font>

522
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:59,577
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I have been
at this all day.</b></i></font>

523
00:19:59,657 --> 00:20:01,659
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you said we don't
have much time.</b></i></font>

524
00:20:01,742 --> 00:20:03,119
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why don't you
just bluff the guy</b></i></font>

525
00:20:03,202 --> 00:20:04,545
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>into giving you
whatever you need?</b></i></font>

526
00:20:04,620 --> 00:20:05,997
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because we've only
got one shot at this.</b></i></font>

527
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:08,924
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The more information I have, the better
chance a bluff is going to work.</b></i></font>

528
00:20:11,293 --> 00:20:13,045
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, what's going on?</b></i></font>

529
00:20:13,129 --> 00:20:15,097
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It isn't like you to stay
in and make phone calls</b></i></font>

530
00:20:15,172 --> 00:20:17,971
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>instead of confronting
someone face-to-face.</b></i></font>

531
00:20:20,886 --> 00:20:24,390
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What if I can't do it and Mike
doesn't get into the Bar?</b></i></font>

532
00:20:24,473 --> 00:20:25,895
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How can you say that?</b></i></font>

533
00:20:25,975 --> 00:20:29,070
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You are the best poker
player I have ever seen.</b></i></font>

534
00:20:29,812 --> 00:20:31,314
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You can do it.</b></i></font>

535
00:20:36,152 --> 00:20:38,701
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't think
you understand, Donna.</b></i></font>

536
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:41,623
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>A bluff only works
if he's dirty.</b></i></font>

537
00:20:41,699 --> 00:20:43,542
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What if the guy
really is clean?</b></i></font>

538
00:20:43,617 --> 00:20:46,791
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, Gibbs got him off the committee.
He's not clean.</b></i></font>

539
00:20:47,538 --> 00:20:49,381
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now, enough is enough.</b></i></font>

540
00:20:49,457 --> 00:20:51,130
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Go do what you do.</b></i></font>

541
00:20:58,048 --> 00:21:00,801
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, you mind
telling me what this is?</b></i></font>

542
00:21:02,052 --> 00:21:03,099
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Where did you get that?</b></i></font>

543
00:21:03,179 --> 00:21:05,773
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That is a lawsuit against
Donna's new business.</b></i></font>

544
00:21:05,848 --> 00:21:06,848
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know what it is.</b></i></font>

545
00:21:06,891 --> 00:21:08,313
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, why haven't you
told her about it yet?</b></i></font>

546
00:21:08,392 --> 00:21:10,440
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because she's going to
think that I blew it</b></i></font>

547
00:21:10,519 --> 00:21:12,112
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because I was upset
about Tara.</b></i></font>

548
00:21:12,188 --> 00:21:15,317
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, did you go full-blown
you on some poor bastard</b></i></font>

549
00:21:15,399 --> 00:21:17,242
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and ruin Donna's
chance at success?</b></i></font>

550
00:21:17,318 --> 00:21:19,571
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Gretchen, I went there
in good faith</b></i></font>

551
00:21:19,653 --> 00:21:21,030
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to get a settlement,
and I was ambushed.</b></i></font>

552
00:21:21,113 --> 00:21:22,365
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I swear.</b></i></font>

553
00:21:22,448 --> 00:21:23,791
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then you need
to fix it.</b></i></font>

554
00:21:23,866 --> 00:21:25,413
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I can't.
Why not?</b></i></font>

555
00:21:25,493 --> 00:21:27,871
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I cannot stop
thinking about Tara.</b></i></font>

556
00:21:28,370 --> 00:21:30,372
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We got into a huge fight.</b></i></font>

557
00:21:31,332 --> 00:21:34,962
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I was such an asshole.</b></i></font>

558
00:21:35,044 --> 00:21:37,012
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So I went to apologize.</b></i></font>

559
00:21:37,463 --> 00:21:39,056
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She said she wasn't sure
she could stay with me</b></i></font>

560
00:21:39,131 --> 00:21:41,509
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I haven't
heard from her since.</b></i></font>

561
00:21:41,592 --> 00:21:43,765
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So now, instead of not
knowing how to fix things</b></i></font>

562
00:21:43,844 --> 00:21:44,845
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>with one woman
in my life,</b></i></font>

563
00:21:44,929 --> 00:21:46,602
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't know how to
fix things with the other.</b></i></font>

564
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:49,058
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, I was married
a long time.</b></i></font>

565
00:21:49,141 --> 00:21:52,236
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'll tell you, Carl
and I had some doozies.</b></i></font>

566
00:21:52,436 --> 00:21:53,813
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tell you the truth,
I wasn't always sure</b></i></font>

567
00:21:53,896 --> 00:21:55,864
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>we were going
to pull through.</b></i></font>

568
00:21:55,940 --> 00:21:58,910
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But we always did, because
we loved each other.</b></i></font>

569
00:22:00,903 --> 00:22:02,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What if she
doesn't love me anymore?</b></i></font>

570
00:22:02,905 --> 00:22:05,533
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It doesn't turn off
like that, Louis.</b></i></font>

571
00:22:05,658 --> 00:22:09,037
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And from where I'm standing,
you're worth loving.</b></i></font>

572
00:22:10,955 --> 00:22:13,879
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now, do you think
you can fix this thing</b></i></font>

573
00:22:13,958 --> 00:22:15,585
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>or do you need me
to get us some help?</b></i></font>

574
00:22:17,002 --> 00:22:19,130
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't need any help.</b></i></font>

575
00:22:20,422 --> 00:22:23,517
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm going to blow those guys
out of the water.</b></i></font>

576
00:22:29,723 --> 00:22:31,441
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Walter Samson?
Yes?</b></i></font>

577
00:22:31,517 --> 00:22:32,643
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I saw you out there.</b></i></font>

578
00:22:32,726 --> 00:22:34,444
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>First time playing?</b></i></font>

579
00:22:34,728 --> 00:22:35,854
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm sorry,
do I know you?</b></i></font>

580
00:22:35,938 --> 00:22:37,778
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The question is, "How do
you know Anita Gibbs?"</b></i></font>

581
00:22:37,815 --> 00:22:40,568
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because you gave her your seat on
the character and fitness committee</b></i></font>

582
00:22:40,651 --> 00:22:42,995
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and the woman who prosecuted Mike
Ross has no business being there.</b></i></font>

583
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,367
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And who is Mike Ross?</b></i></font>

584
00:22:44,446 --> 00:22:46,744
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I get it.
We're going that way, huh?</b></i></font>

585
00:22:46,824 --> 00:22:49,703
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He's the reason Gibbs strong-armed
you into giving up that seat.</b></i></font>

586
00:22:49,785 --> 00:22:51,207
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I gave up that seat
because I wanted to</b></i></font>

587
00:22:51,287 --> 00:22:52,487
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>spend more time
with my family.</b></i></font>

588
00:22:52,496 --> 00:22:53,543
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bullshit.</b></i></font>

589
00:22:53,622 --> 00:22:55,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She found out whatever dirty
little secret you're hiding.</b></i></font>

590
00:22:55,499 --> 00:22:56,625
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you don't come
clean with me,</b></i></font>

591
00:22:56,709 --> 00:22:58,711
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm going to find out what it is
and I'm going to squeeze harder.</b></i></font>

592
00:22:58,794 --> 00:22:59,886
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't know who you are,</b></i></font>

593
00:22:59,962 --> 00:23:01,214
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but it must be nice
living in a world</b></i></font>

594
00:23:01,297 --> 00:23:03,766
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>where everyone has a weak
spot and is unethical.</b></i></font>

595
00:23:03,841 --> 00:23:05,969
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But in this case,
I took a leave of absence</b></i></font>

596
00:23:06,051 --> 00:23:08,304
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I replaced myself
with a worthy attorney.</b></i></font>

597
00:23:08,387 --> 00:23:11,231
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So you can look for a
pressure point all you want,</b></i></font>

598
00:23:11,307 --> 00:23:12,809
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I'm sorry
to inform you</b></i></font>

599
00:23:12,892 --> 00:23:14,012
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you're not going
to find one.</b></i></font>

600
00:23:15,019 --> 00:23:17,693
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You want to know who I am?
My name is Harvey Specter.</b></i></font>

601
00:23:17,771 --> 00:23:19,569
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you can say you never
heard of Mike Ross,</b></i></font>

602
00:23:19,648 --> 00:23:21,241
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I know you heard of me.</b></i></font>

603
00:23:21,317 --> 00:23:22,739
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So maybe
she didn't blackmail you.</b></i></font>

604
00:23:22,818 --> 00:23:24,616
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Maybe she promised
to do something for you.</b></i></font>

605
00:23:24,695 --> 00:23:26,868
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Either way, I'm going
to find out what it is,</b></i></font>

606
00:23:26,947 --> 00:23:28,699
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and you're going to wish
you told me right now.</b></i></font>

607
00:23:28,782 --> 00:23:30,204
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You think you're
showing strength,</b></i></font>

608
00:23:30,284 --> 00:23:32,582
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but intimidation
is only weakness.</b></i></font>

609
00:23:32,661 --> 00:23:35,084
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And for your information,
I never met Anita Gibbs</b></i></font>

610
00:23:35,164 --> 00:23:37,667
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>until the day I appointed her
as my replacement.</b></i></font>

611
00:23:44,882 --> 00:23:46,555
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>When I first met
Mike Ross,</b></i></font>

612
00:23:46,634 --> 00:23:49,433
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I thought he was like every
other criminal I work with.</b></i></font>

613
00:23:49,511 --> 00:23:52,640
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>An entitled fraud who spent
his life cutting corners.</b></i></font>

614
00:23:52,723 --> 00:23:53,770
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'm here
to tell you,</b></i></font>

615
00:23:53,849 --> 00:23:56,693
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>he went into prison one man
and he walked out another.</b></i></font>

616
00:23:56,769 --> 00:23:58,646
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And in my professional
opinion,</b></i></font>

617
00:23:58,729 --> 00:23:59,821
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>he has the integrity</b></i></font>

618
00:23:59,897 --> 00:24:01,695
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to serve his community
as a lawyer.</b></i></font>

619
00:24:01,774 --> 00:24:04,118
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>While I don't doubt
your sincerity, Mr. Rowe,</b></i></font>

620
00:24:04,193 --> 00:24:05,593
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>just because he was
able to fool you</b></i></font>

621
00:24:05,653 --> 00:24:07,200
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>doesn't mean he's going to
be able to fool this board.</b></i></font>

622
00:24:07,279 --> 00:24:08,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's Dr. Rowe.</b></i></font>

623
00:24:08,906 --> 00:24:11,750
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm glad you were the one
who responded to my statement.</b></i></font>

624
00:24:11,825 --> 00:24:12,825
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And why is that?</b></i></font>

625
00:24:12,868 --> 00:24:15,462
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because you tried to paint a
false picture of his release</b></i></font>

626
00:24:15,537 --> 00:24:17,164
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I'm here to set
the record straight.</b></i></font>

627
00:24:17,247 --> 00:24:18,294
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The record is straight.</b></i></font>

628
00:24:18,374 --> 00:24:20,547
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you're not qualified to talk
about the deal that he made.</b></i></font>

629
00:24:20,626 --> 00:24:22,299
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No. We're going
to hear this.</b></i></font>

630
00:24:22,378 --> 00:24:23,470
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you.</b></i></font>

631
00:24:23,545 --> 00:24:26,970
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's true Mr. Ross entered into
an early release agreement,</b></i></font>

632
00:24:27,049 --> 00:24:29,427
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but it's also true
that he stayed in longer</b></i></font>

633
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:31,638
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>than he had to,
to keep his cellmate safe.</b></i></font>

634
00:24:31,720 --> 00:24:32,846
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And while he was there,</b></i></font>

635
00:24:32,930 --> 00:24:35,353
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>he risked his own life
to prevent a violent man</b></i></font>

636
00:24:35,432 --> 00:24:36,979
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>from falsely
obtaining parole.</b></i></font>

637
00:24:37,059 --> 00:24:39,653
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And for all we know, he did
that for self-serving reasons.</b></i></font>

638
00:24:39,728 --> 00:24:41,888
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And for all I know, that's
what you're doing right now.</b></i></font>

639
00:24:41,897 --> 00:24:43,114
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're out of line.</b></i></font>

640
00:24:43,190 --> 00:24:45,033
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not the one
under examination here.</b></i></font>

641
00:24:45,109 --> 00:24:46,281
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Neither am I.</b></i></font>

642
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:47,703
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm a prison psychologist.</b></i></font>

643
00:24:47,778 --> 00:24:48,995
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And in my experience,</b></i></font>

644
00:24:49,071 --> 00:24:52,075
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>self-serving men do not risk
their lives to help people.</b></i></font>

645
00:24:52,157 --> 00:24:56,128
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't call defrauding your
fellow man helping people.</b></i></font>

646
00:24:56,203 --> 00:24:59,207
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I certainly don't
call it having integrity.</b></i></font>

647
00:24:59,289 --> 00:25:03,089
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>With all due respect, ma'am, I'm
done wasting my breath on you,</b></i></font>

648
00:25:03,168 --> 00:25:05,011
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because the purpose
of this hearing</b></i></font>

649
00:25:05,087 --> 00:25:07,089
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>was to determine if
Mike Ross had reformed.</b></i></font>

650
00:25:07,172 --> 00:25:09,049
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But you don't seem
to be interested in that,</b></i></font>

651
00:25:09,133 --> 00:25:10,350
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because you've already
made your mind up.</b></i></font>

652
00:25:10,426 --> 00:25:11,518
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Maybe I have.</b></i></font>

653
00:25:11,593 --> 00:25:13,595
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then maybe you shouldn't
be on this committee,</b></i></font>

654
00:25:13,679 --> 00:25:17,775
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because as I said, in my
professional opinion,</b></i></font>

655
00:25:17,850 --> 00:25:20,649
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>the world could use
a lawyer like Mike Ross.</b></i></font>

656
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:23,364
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if you're looking
for my personal opinion,</b></i></font>

657
00:25:23,439 --> 00:25:24,861
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>he has more integrity
in his little finger</b></i></font>

658
00:25:24,940 --> 00:25:27,739
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>than you have
in your whole body.</b></i></font>

659
00:25:49,548 --> 00:25:50,891
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, where
have you been?</b></i></font>

660
00:25:50,966 --> 00:25:52,092
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've been trying to
level the playing field.</b></i></font>

661
00:25:52,176 --> 00:25:54,474
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's the thing.
We just did.</b></i></font>

662
00:25:54,553 --> 00:25:55,770
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You should have seen
Julius up there.</b></i></font>

663
00:25:55,846 --> 00:25:57,268
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I mean, if those
members vote no</b></i></font>

664
00:25:57,347 --> 00:25:58,707
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>after hearing
what he had to say...</b></i></font>

665
00:25:58,766 --> 00:26:00,359
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It doesn't matter
what he had to say.</b></i></font>

666
00:26:02,436 --> 00:26:04,655
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You haven't found a way to get
Gibbs off that committee.</b></i></font>

667
00:26:05,481 --> 00:26:06,528
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No.</b></i></font>

668
00:26:13,989 --> 00:26:15,241
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm sorry, Mike.</b></i></font>

669
00:26:15,324 --> 00:26:16,997
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't have to
be sorry, Harvey.</b></i></font>

670
00:26:17,701 --> 00:26:20,830
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She warned us that she'd never
let me get into the Bar.</b></i></font>

671
00:26:21,455 --> 00:26:23,332
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We just didn't listen.</b></i></font>

672
00:26:25,834 --> 00:26:26,835
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Listen to me.</b></i></font>

673
00:26:27,836 --> 00:26:29,356
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This vote isn't
until tomorrow morning.</b></i></font>

674
00:26:29,421 --> 00:26:31,301
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's still time for us
to think of something.</b></i></font>

675
00:26:31,340 --> 00:26:32,808
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, you keep trying,
Harvey.</b></i></font>

676
00:26:34,134 --> 00:26:35,977
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've got something else
I need to take care of.</b></i></font>

677
00:26:42,267 --> 00:26:43,439
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's going on?</b></i></font>

678
00:26:44,019 --> 00:26:45,612
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Gretchen said you wanted to
talk to me about the patent.</b></i></font>

679
00:26:45,687 --> 00:26:46,813
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you guys
doing here?</b></i></font>

680
00:26:46,897 --> 00:26:48,240
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I went back
to them, Donna.</b></i></font>

681
00:26:48,315 --> 00:26:50,784
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And the reason I asked Stu
and Benjamin to be here was</b></i></font>

682
00:26:50,859 --> 00:26:52,782
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>so that you'd know
that I didn't shit the bed.</b></i></font>

683
00:26:52,861 --> 00:26:54,909
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Are you telling me you couldn't
get them to back off the lawsuit?</b></i></font>

684
00:26:54,988 --> 00:26:56,956
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He's telling you we won't be
able to patent The Donna at all.</b></i></font>

685
00:26:57,032 --> 00:26:58,079
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?</b></i></font>

686
00:26:58,158 --> 00:27:00,478
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donna, they weren't authorized
to let us partner with them.</b></i></font>

687
00:27:00,536 --> 00:27:02,129
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's what I sent you over
there to take care of.</b></i></font>

688
00:27:02,204 --> 00:27:03,296
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know.</b></i></font>

689
00:27:03,372 --> 00:27:05,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And then they said they would fight
us to the ends of the earth.</b></i></font>

690
00:27:05,499 --> 00:27:07,217
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Sol pulled out
every trick in the book</b></i></font>

691
00:27:07,292 --> 00:27:09,590
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I got them
to make you an offer.</b></i></font>

692
00:27:09,670 --> 00:27:11,047
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>An offer sounds
like a buy-out.</b></i></font>

693
00:27:11,130 --> 00:27:12,382
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's because
it is a buy-out.</b></i></font>

694
00:27:12,464 --> 00:27:13,984
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>With a special provision
that allows us</b></i></font>

695
00:27:14,049 --> 00:27:15,529
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to produce The Donna
for in-house use.</b></i></font>

696
00:27:15,551 --> 00:27:16,552
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's not good enough.</b></i></font>

697
00:27:16,635 --> 00:27:17,887
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donna, we're talking
about a lot of money.</b></i></font>

698
00:27:17,970 --> 00:27:19,563
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't care
about the money, Stu.</b></i></font>

699
00:27:19,638 --> 00:27:21,356
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I care that Louis
didn't fight for me.</b></i></font>

700
00:27:21,431 --> 00:27:23,399
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I did fight for you,
Donna. I swear.</b></i></font>

701
00:27:23,475 --> 00:27:25,022
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They've got us
dead to rights.</b></i></font>

702
00:27:25,102 --> 00:27:26,274
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's nothing more
I can do.</b></i></font>

703
00:27:26,353 --> 00:27:28,572
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bullshit. Louis Litt does
not roll over for anybody.</b></i></font>

704
00:27:28,647 --> 00:27:29,944
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He didn't
roll over, Donna.</b></i></font>

705
00:27:30,023 --> 00:27:30,990
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I went over it
with Benjamin,</b></i></font>

706
00:27:31,066 --> 00:27:32,784
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and we can't get
the overlap under 30%</b></i></font>

707
00:27:32,860 --> 00:27:34,533
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I also ran it
by my own attorney</b></i></font>

708
00:27:34,611 --> 00:27:36,651
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and he was shocked at what
Louis was able to get us.</b></i></font>

709
00:27:37,281 --> 00:27:39,249
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So you're telling me
you want to take it.</b></i></font>

710
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,372
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We do.</b></i></font>

711
00:27:42,452 --> 00:27:44,250
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But The Donna
wouldn't even exist</b></i></font>

712
00:27:44,329 --> 00:27:45,330
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>without you,
and we're partners.</b></i></font>

713
00:27:45,414 --> 00:27:48,088
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, if you don't want to,
then we won't.</b></i></font>

714
00:27:54,131 --> 00:27:56,054
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm going to need
to think about it.</b></i></font>

715
00:28:12,274 --> 00:28:13,400
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's that?</b></i></font>

716
00:28:13,483 --> 00:28:14,735
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Liberty Rail.</b></i></font>

717
00:28:14,818 --> 00:28:16,365
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I tried to give it
to you once before.</b></i></font>

718
00:28:16,445 --> 00:28:17,617
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You wouldn't take it.</b></i></font>

719
00:28:17,696 --> 00:28:19,039
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You said it should
come without strings.</b></i></font>

720
00:28:19,114 --> 00:28:21,037
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, here it is.
No strings.</b></i></font>

721
00:28:21,116 --> 00:28:23,460
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's still got strings
and you know it.</b></i></font>

722
00:28:23,535 --> 00:28:24,752
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You want me to let
Mike in the Bar.</b></i></font>

723
00:28:24,828 --> 00:28:25,920
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I do.</b></i></font>

724
00:28:25,996 --> 00:28:28,090
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'm giving you this
whether you do that or not.</b></i></font>

725
00:28:28,874 --> 00:28:29,921
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And why would you do that?</b></i></font>

726
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:32,378
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I'm hoping if I
showed you I could change,</b></i></font>

727
00:28:32,461 --> 00:28:35,180
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>maybe you'd believe
he could, too.</b></i></font>

728
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,222
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You for him.</b></i></font>

729
00:28:42,596 --> 00:28:43,688
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?</b></i></font>

730
00:28:46,350 --> 00:28:48,398
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tomorrow morning,
I'm going to ask Mike</b></i></font>

731
00:28:48,477 --> 00:28:50,070
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>if anyone knew
he was a fraud</b></i></font>

732
00:28:50,145 --> 00:28:52,022
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>while he was at
Pearson Specter.</b></i></font>

733
00:28:52,105 --> 00:28:55,279
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He admits you knew,
I'll let him in the Bar.</b></i></font>

734
00:28:55,359 --> 00:28:56,781
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I do that,
they'll kick me out.</b></i></font>

735
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:58,908
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's what
"you for him" means.</b></i></font>

736
00:28:59,488 --> 00:29:01,411
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You said you'd do it
for him once.</b></i></font>

737
00:29:01,490 --> 00:29:03,771
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This is your chance to put your
money where your mouth is.</b></i></font>

738
00:29:03,784 --> 00:29:04,876
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He won't go for it.</b></i></font>

739
00:29:04,952 --> 00:29:06,920
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He wants to be a lawyer
so bad he can taste it.</b></i></font>

740
00:29:06,995 --> 00:29:08,793
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You can make him
go for it.</b></i></font>

741
00:29:10,332 --> 00:29:12,585
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Just remember,</b></i></font>

742
00:29:12,668 --> 00:29:15,091
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you didn't like
being too late last time.</b></i></font>

743
00:29:15,170 --> 00:29:17,389
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're not too late
this time.</b></i></font>

744
00:29:21,593 --> 00:29:23,766
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Good. You're both here.</b></i></font>

745
00:29:23,845 --> 00:29:25,017
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thanks for staying.</b></i></font>

746
00:29:25,097 --> 00:29:27,065
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Of course we stayed. Your
message said it was urgent.</b></i></font>

747
00:29:27,140 --> 00:29:28,767
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's going on? Is there a
problem with the settlement?</b></i></font>

748
00:29:28,850 --> 00:29:29,851
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No.</b></i></font>

749
00:29:29,935 --> 00:29:32,779
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I gave Oliver my word that
I would tell you the truth.</b></i></font>

750
00:29:32,854 --> 00:29:33,821
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, I'm here
to tell you the truth.</b></i></font>

751
00:29:33,897 --> 00:29:35,319
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The truth
about what?</b></i></font>

752
00:29:35,399 --> 00:29:36,446
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I made a deal.</b></i></font>

753
00:29:36,525 --> 00:29:38,744
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>A quid pro quo that we would
handle the miners' case</b></i></font>

754
00:29:38,819 --> 00:29:40,992
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>in exchange for the chance
to be admitted to the Bar.</b></i></font>

755
00:29:42,030 --> 00:29:43,953
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Are you goddamn
kidding me?</b></i></font>

756
00:29:44,032 --> 00:29:46,626
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I asked you point blank
if something was going on</b></i></font>

757
00:29:46,702 --> 00:29:47,919
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and you lied to my face?</b></i></font>

758
00:29:47,995 --> 00:29:49,042
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Nathan, I'm sorry.</b></i></font>

759
00:29:49,121 --> 00:29:51,123
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I didn't want to tell you until
there was something to tell.</b></i></font>

760
00:29:51,206 --> 00:29:52,753
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You weren't going to tell me
until you got away with it.</b></i></font>

761
00:29:52,833 --> 00:29:53,833
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No. I wasn't.</b></i></font>

762
00:29:53,875 --> 00:29:55,377
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But as it turns out, I'm not
going to get away with it.</b></i></font>

763
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:56,552
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm telling you anyway.</b></i></font>

764
00:29:57,212 --> 00:29:59,135
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're fired.
Nathan, please.</b></i></font>

765
00:29:59,214 --> 00:30:00,966
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't give a shit what's about
to come out of your mouth.</b></i></font>

766
00:30:01,049 --> 00:30:04,269
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Clean out your office and never
show your face around here again.</b></i></font>

767
00:30:04,344 --> 00:30:06,312
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Wait. Don't do it.</b></i></font>

768
00:30:06,388 --> 00:30:07,640
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Did you hear
what he said?</b></i></font>

769
00:30:07,723 --> 00:30:08,923
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He lied.
Not once, not twice...</b></i></font>

770
00:30:08,974 --> 00:30:10,317
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't care,
because we need him.</b></i></font>

771
00:30:10,392 --> 00:30:11,814
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We don't need him.</b></i></font>

772
00:30:11,893 --> 00:30:14,442
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Sofia needed him and she got
me, and look what happened.</b></i></font>

773
00:30:15,439 --> 00:30:17,407
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, Nathan, that was
some shady shit he pulled.</b></i></font>

774
00:30:17,482 --> 00:30:20,361
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But you've got to be blind if you
can't see that he actually cares.</b></i></font>

775
00:30:20,444 --> 00:30:23,072
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I don't remember us beating
down a place like Velocity Data</b></i></font>

776
00:30:23,155 --> 00:30:24,327
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>before he got here.</b></i></font>

777
00:30:24,406 --> 00:30:26,374
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, if it's all the same to
you, I'd like him to stay.</b></i></font>

778
00:30:26,450 --> 00:30:28,168
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, it's not all the
same to me, Oliver.</b></i></font>

779
00:30:28,243 --> 00:30:29,620
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's up to me.</b></i></font>

780
00:30:29,703 --> 00:30:32,172
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Not to the person that kept it
from me as much as Mike did.</b></i></font>

781
00:30:32,247 --> 00:30:34,750
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He didn't keep it
from you, Nathan.</b></i></font>

782
00:30:35,083 --> 00:30:37,461
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He said that if I didn't
tell you, he would.</b></i></font>

783
00:30:38,086 --> 00:30:39,338
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So here I am.</b></i></font>

784
00:30:39,421 --> 00:30:41,594
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I know that I don't
have a leg to stand on,</b></i></font>

785
00:30:41,673 --> 00:30:45,268
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I'd like to stay.</b></i></font>

786
00:30:50,223 --> 00:30:52,851
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Monday morning, you better start
putting your money where your mouth is</b></i></font>

787
00:30:52,934 --> 00:30:55,357
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and find us
another $50,000 case.</b></i></font>

788
00:31:08,867 --> 00:31:10,460
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis,
do you have a minute?</b></i></font>

789
00:31:11,411 --> 00:31:12,628
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Sure, Harvey.</b></i></font>

790
00:31:12,704 --> 00:31:13,921
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't know how
much you know about</b></i></font>

791
00:31:13,997 --> 00:31:15,249
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>what's going on
with Mike's hearing.</b></i></font>

792
00:31:15,332 --> 00:31:17,334
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Enough to know that look on your
face means it's not going well.</b></i></font>

793
00:31:17,417 --> 00:31:18,464
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's not.</b></i></font>

794
00:31:18,543 --> 00:31:19,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I may have
a way to change it,</b></i></font>

795
00:31:19,836 --> 00:31:21,588
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I wanted to run it
by my partner first,</b></i></font>

796
00:31:21,671 --> 00:31:24,265
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because it may mean that
I need a little time off.</b></i></font>

797
00:31:24,341 --> 00:31:26,059
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean,
a little time off?</b></i></font>

798
00:31:26,134 --> 00:31:27,761
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I mean Gibbs
offered me a deal.</b></i></font>

799
00:31:27,844 --> 00:31:31,064
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike goes on record admitting
I knew he was a fraud,</b></i></font>

800
00:31:31,139 --> 00:31:32,561
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>she'll vote to
let him in the Bar.</b></i></font>

801
00:31:32,641 --> 00:31:33,688
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Are you insane?</b></i></font>

802
00:31:33,767 --> 00:31:35,735
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You do that, it won't
be a little time off.</b></i></font>

803
00:31:35,811 --> 00:31:37,028
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You'll get disbarred.</b></i></font>

804
00:31:37,104 --> 00:31:38,572
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And by then,
he'll be a lawyer,</b></i></font>

805
00:31:38,647 --> 00:31:41,400
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and we can argue that he said
that just to appease Gibbs.</b></i></font>

806
00:31:41,483 --> 00:31:42,530
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bullshit.</b></i></font>

807
00:31:42,609 --> 00:31:44,611
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You do this, two out of three
names on that wall will be gone,</b></i></font>

808
00:31:44,694 --> 00:31:45,991
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I won't be able to
keep this firm going.</b></i></font>

809
00:31:46,071 --> 00:31:48,995
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if you can't, we'll have done
it for Mike. Zane will hire you.</b></i></font>

810
00:31:49,074 --> 00:31:50,792
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't want
to go to Zane's.</b></i></font>

811
00:31:50,867 --> 00:31:52,494
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want to do what we said
we were going to do</b></i></font>

812
00:31:52,577 --> 00:31:53,578
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and rebuild this
place together.</b></i></font>

813
00:31:53,662 --> 00:31:54,663
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, I owe him.</b></i></font>

814
00:31:54,746 --> 00:31:56,589
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, what about what you owe me?
You said we were partners.</b></i></font>

815
00:31:56,665 --> 00:31:59,009
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We are partners, which is why
I came to you with this.</b></i></font>

816
00:31:59,084 --> 00:32:00,085
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No.</b></i></font>

817
00:32:00,168 --> 00:32:01,966
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You didn't come
to ask my permission,</b></i></font>

818
00:32:02,045 --> 00:32:03,763
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you came to tell me that
you were going to do this.</b></i></font>

819
00:32:03,839 --> 00:32:04,931
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And what if I did?</b></i></font>

820
00:32:05,006 --> 00:32:06,349
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then you're not just an
asshole, you're an idiot.</b></i></font>

821
00:32:06,425 --> 00:32:07,472
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because there's
no way Mike Ross</b></i></font>

822
00:32:07,551 --> 00:32:09,053
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>ever agrees to
trading you for him.</b></i></font>

823
00:32:09,136 --> 00:32:10,353
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, I'll make him agree.</b></i></font>

824
00:32:10,429 --> 00:32:11,931
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, you won't.</b></i></font>

825
00:32:12,264 --> 00:32:13,311
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike.</b></i></font>

826
00:32:13,390 --> 00:32:15,563
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, whatever deal she's offering
you, I'm not going to take it.</b></i></font>

827
00:32:15,642 --> 00:32:16,609
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't even
know what it is.</b></i></font>

828
00:32:16,685 --> 00:32:17,902
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't care
what it is.</b></i></font>

829
00:32:17,978 --> 00:32:20,151
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not getting into the Bar if
it means getting you kicked out.</b></i></font>

830
00:32:20,230 --> 00:32:21,823
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, she wants me.
She always has.</b></i></font>

831
00:32:21,898 --> 00:32:23,866
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, Harvey.
She wants both of us.</b></i></font>

832
00:32:23,942 --> 00:32:26,491
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And she's not going to stop
until she gets both of us.</b></i></font>

833
00:32:26,570 --> 00:32:28,163
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't know that.
Yes, I do.</b></i></font>

834
00:32:28,238 --> 00:32:29,285
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if you
don't get that,</b></i></font>

835
00:32:29,364 --> 00:32:31,124
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>then she's got you
right where she wants you.</b></i></font>

836
00:32:31,241 --> 00:32:32,914
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So you're just going
to sit there tomorrow</b></i></font>

837
00:32:32,993 --> 00:32:34,633
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and let her take
everything away from you?</b></i></font>

838
00:32:34,661 --> 00:32:36,163
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She's not
taking anything away.</b></i></font>

839
00:32:36,246 --> 00:32:38,169
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She's keeping things
exactly the way they are.</b></i></font>

840
00:32:38,248 --> 00:32:39,591
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You mean working
for that clinic.</b></i></font>

841
00:32:39,666 --> 00:32:42,044
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I'm lucky to still
have a job at that clinic.</b></i></font>

842
00:32:43,253 --> 00:32:44,379
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So tomorrow morning,</b></i></font>

843
00:32:44,463 --> 00:32:46,807
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm going to go in there
with my head held high.</b></i></font>

844
00:32:46,882 --> 00:32:51,934
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But what I'm not going to do is let her
strip you of everything that you are.</b></i></font>

845
00:32:58,685 --> 00:33:00,483
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, he's right.</b></i></font>

846
00:33:00,687 --> 00:33:02,030
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Let it go.</b></i></font>

847
00:33:18,205 --> 00:33:19,205
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Whatever it is, Donna...</b></i></font>

848
00:33:19,247 --> 00:33:20,840
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I know you're in
a rough place right now.</b></i></font>

849
00:33:20,916 --> 00:33:23,669
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But whatever's going to happen
with Mike is going to happen.</b></i></font>

850
00:33:23,752 --> 00:33:25,504
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You've done
everything you can.</b></i></font>

851
00:33:25,587 --> 00:33:27,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm tired of
putting my wants on hold.</b></i></font>

852
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:29,591
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What is it?</b></i></font>

853
00:33:29,674 --> 00:33:31,972
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You know about my product
with Benjamin.</b></i></font>

854
00:33:32,052 --> 00:33:33,052
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I do.</b></i></font>

855
00:33:33,094 --> 00:33:35,847
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, it turns out
we have a 32.5% overlap</b></i></font>

856
00:33:35,931 --> 00:33:38,559
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>on our software
with another company's.</b></i></font>

857
00:33:38,642 --> 00:33:39,939
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They refused to budge,</b></i></font>

858
00:33:40,018 --> 00:33:44,194
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and Louis said he pulled out every
trick in the book to get us this.</b></i></font>

859
00:33:48,693 --> 00:33:51,242
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Can you get it under 30%? No.</b></i></font>

860
00:33:52,614 --> 00:33:54,082
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then take the money.</b></i></font>

861
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:57,623
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't want the money.</b></i></font>

862
00:33:57,702 --> 00:33:59,625
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donna.
I want something more.</b></i></font>

863
00:34:00,789 --> 00:34:02,109
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I've never
said that out loud.</b></i></font>

864
00:34:02,165 --> 00:34:04,884
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I can't pretend
that's not true anymore.</b></i></font>

865
00:34:08,296 --> 00:34:10,173
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean, "more"?</b></i></font>

866
00:34:11,466 --> 00:34:12,968
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't know.</b></i></font>

867
00:34:18,139 --> 00:34:21,143
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I guess I'm going to
have to figure that out.</b></i></font>

868
00:34:29,442 --> 00:34:30,739
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Good night, Harvey.</b></i></font>

869
00:34:30,944 --> 00:34:32,867
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'll see you tomorrow
at the hearing.</b></i></font>

870
00:34:41,871 --> 00:34:44,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mr. Ross, we are prepared to
hear your final statement.</b></i></font>

871
00:34:44,499 --> 00:34:47,173
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Before we do, I have
one last question.</b></i></font>

872
00:34:47,294 --> 00:34:51,094
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mr. Ross, you say you're a changed
man and you care about the truth,</b></i></font>

873
00:34:51,172 --> 00:34:54,301
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I want to know if you're
capable of telling the truth.</b></i></font>

874
00:34:54,676 --> 00:34:56,474
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So I'm going to
ask you a question</b></i></font>

875
00:34:56,553 --> 00:34:59,181
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I suggest that you consider
your answer very carefully,</b></i></font>

876
00:34:59,264 --> 00:35:00,686
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because as far
as I'm concerned,</b></i></font>

877
00:35:00,765 --> 00:35:03,985
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>your answer will determine whether
or not you become a lawyer.</b></i></font>

878
00:35:05,520 --> 00:35:08,945
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>During your time at
Pearson Specter Litt,</b></i></font>

879
00:35:09,024 --> 00:35:13,074
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>did anyone there have knowledge of
the fact that you were a fraud?</b></i></font>

880
00:35:18,366 --> 00:35:19,663
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mr. Ross.</b></i></font>

881
00:35:19,993 --> 00:35:21,791
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Did anyone else know?</b></i></font>

882
00:35:24,956 --> 00:35:26,208
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I knew.</b></i></font>

883
00:35:28,710 --> 00:35:31,964
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if you're looking for a
scalp, you can have mine.</b></i></font>

884
00:35:32,339 --> 00:35:34,558
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I was under the
impression that this hearing</b></i></font>

885
00:35:34,633 --> 00:35:36,306
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>was not about
my old firm,</b></i></font>

886
00:35:36,384 --> 00:35:39,479
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but whether or not Mr.
Ross should be a lawyer.</b></i></font>

887
00:35:40,972 --> 00:35:42,019
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I say he should.</b></i></font>

888
00:35:42,098 --> 00:35:43,475
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It doesn't
matter what you say.</b></i></font>

889
00:35:43,558 --> 00:35:45,401
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He's already had
someone testify for him.</b></i></font>

890
00:35:45,477 --> 00:35:47,037
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not here
to talk about him.</b></i></font>

891
00:35:47,687 --> 00:35:48,904
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm here to talk
about someone else.</b></i></font>

892
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:50,232
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Someone else has
nothing to do with...</b></i></font>

893
00:35:50,315 --> 00:35:51,783
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'd like to
hear this.</b></i></font>

894
00:35:51,858 --> 00:35:53,110
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Fifteen years ago,</b></i></font>

895
00:35:53,193 --> 00:35:57,994
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>a young woman was arrested for illegally
obtaining prescription drugs.</b></i></font>

896
00:35:58,073 --> 00:36:00,075
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Turns out she had
chronic pain</b></i></font>

897
00:36:00,158 --> 00:36:01,660
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and didn't want to drop out
of med school,</b></i></font>

898
00:36:01,743 --> 00:36:03,711
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>possibly never to return.</b></i></font>

899
00:36:03,787 --> 00:36:06,631
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, she stole a couple
of prescription pads</b></i></font>

900
00:36:06,706 --> 00:36:08,834
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>from the hospital
where she was interning.</b></i></font>

901
00:36:08,917 --> 00:36:12,091
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>A crime with a mandatory
sentence of seven years.</b></i></font>

902
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:15,674
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But instead of throwing
the book at her,</b></i></font>

903
00:36:15,757 --> 00:36:18,260
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>the prosecuting attorney
showed mercy,</b></i></font>

904
00:36:18,843 --> 00:36:21,141
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>had the charges knocked
down to a misdemeanor,</b></i></font>

905
00:36:21,221 --> 00:36:24,350
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>recommended probation,
and sealed the records.</b></i></font>

906
00:36:24,432 --> 00:36:25,775
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's a touching story,</b></i></font>

907
00:36:25,850 --> 00:36:27,693
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I don't see
what a random attorney</b></i></font>

908
00:36:27,769 --> 00:36:29,191
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>has to do with
these proceedings.</b></i></font>

909
00:36:29,270 --> 00:36:32,820
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She's not talking about a random attorney.
She's talking about me.</b></i></font>

910
00:36:33,942 --> 00:36:36,286
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But just because
I showed compassion once</b></i></font>

911
00:36:36,361 --> 00:36:38,363
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>doesn't mean
he deserves it now.</b></i></font>

912
00:36:38,446 --> 00:36:39,789
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Maybe he doesn't.</b></i></font>

913
00:36:39,864 --> 00:36:42,083
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But that young woman
is now an ER doctor.</b></i></font>

914
00:36:42,158 --> 00:36:43,785
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She saves lives.</b></i></font>

915
00:36:43,952 --> 00:36:47,502
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And the world is a better
place because you saved hers.</b></i></font>

916
00:36:48,790 --> 00:36:50,667
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you, Ms. Pearson.</b></i></font>

917
00:36:50,834 --> 00:36:52,131
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mr. Ross?</b></i></font>

918
00:36:57,590 --> 00:37:00,389
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't think I can add
anything to that.</b></i></font>

919
00:37:01,469 --> 00:37:03,142
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've made my case.</b></i></font>

920
00:37:03,805 --> 00:37:05,807
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I leave the choice to you.</b></i></font>

921
00:37:07,308 --> 00:37:08,776
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then this hearing
has concluded.</b></i></font>

922
00:37:09,561 --> 00:37:10,733
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We will deliberate
and let you know</b></i></font>

923
00:37:10,812 --> 00:37:12,530
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>our decision
by day's end.</b></i></font>

924
00:37:12,605 --> 00:37:13,731
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you.</b></i></font>

925
00:37:25,869 --> 00:37:27,621
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, what do we do now?</b></i></font>

926
00:37:27,704 --> 00:37:30,082
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They said they would let us
know by the end of the day.</b></i></font>

927
00:37:30,165 --> 00:37:31,291
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So we wait.</b></i></font>

928
00:37:31,374 --> 00:37:32,466
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, it is the end of
the day, which means...</b></i></font>

929
00:37:32,542 --> 00:37:33,589
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It doesn't
mean anything, Louis.</b></i></font>

930
00:37:33,668 --> 00:37:36,717
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Whatever is going on in there,
Seidel's going to fight like hell...</b></i></font>

931
00:37:36,796 --> 00:37:38,196
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's not going to
make a difference.</b></i></font>

932
00:37:39,841 --> 00:37:41,639
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She's never going
to change her mind.</b></i></font>

933
00:37:42,010 --> 00:37:43,432
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I think she will.</b></i></font>

934
00:37:43,511 --> 00:37:44,512
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean?</b></i></font>

935
00:37:44,596 --> 00:37:47,349
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I mean that story
wasn't any old story</b></i></font>

936
00:37:47,432 --> 00:37:49,150
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and that woman
wasn't really a woman.</b></i></font>

937
00:37:49,225 --> 00:37:51,227
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It was a man
named Joseph O'Neal.</b></i></font>

938
00:37:51,311 --> 00:37:53,734
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And it was
Walter Samson's godson.</b></i></font>

939
00:37:54,689 --> 00:37:55,941
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So she did call in
a favor.</b></i></font>

940
00:37:56,024 --> 00:37:57,150
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yes, she did.</b></i></font>

941
00:37:57,233 --> 00:37:59,201
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then we need to get her
kicked off that board.</b></i></font>

942
00:37:59,277 --> 00:38:00,824
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, Harvey.
We don't.</b></i></font>

943
00:38:00,904 --> 00:38:03,874
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I didn't fly all the way
down here to strong-arm that woman.</b></i></font>

944
00:38:03,948 --> 00:38:05,791
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I know the story of
The Wind and The Sun.</b></i></font>

945
00:38:05,867 --> 00:38:06,959
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What the hell
are you talking about?</b></i></font>

946
00:38:07,035 --> 00:38:08,595
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She's talking
about Aesop's fable,</b></i></font>

947
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:11,180
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>which basically says that if you
want a man to take off his coat,</b></i></font>

948
00:38:11,247 --> 00:38:12,715
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you don't blow it off.</b></i></font>

949
00:38:13,416 --> 00:38:15,635
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You make him feel warm and
he'll take it off on his own.</b></i></font>

950
00:38:15,710 --> 00:38:18,008
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's not a strategy,
it's a prayer.</b></i></font>

951
00:38:18,087 --> 00:38:19,967
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, I already admitted
that I knew about Mike</b></i></font>

952
00:38:20,006 --> 00:38:22,805
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I reminded her
of her own compassion.</b></i></font>

953
00:38:22,884 --> 00:38:24,852
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's the best
we're going to do.</b></i></font>

954
00:38:25,303 --> 00:38:26,930
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You know they could
disbar you for that.</b></i></font>

955
00:38:27,013 --> 00:38:28,293
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>In New York,
they might.</b></i></font>

956
00:38:28,348 --> 00:38:30,396
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>In Chicago,
nobody's going to care.</b></i></font>

957
00:38:31,434 --> 00:38:32,560
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you, Jessica.</b></i></font>

958
00:38:32,644 --> 00:38:34,442
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Don't thank me.
Thank Harvey.</b></i></font>

959
00:38:34,521 --> 00:38:36,521
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He's
the one that called me.</b></i></font>

960
00:38:37,565 --> 00:38:38,908
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's Seidel.</b></i></font>

961
00:38:40,610 --> 00:38:41,782
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Hello.</b></i></font>

962
00:38:45,865 --> 00:38:47,367
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'll tell him.</b></i></font>

963
00:38:48,576 --> 00:38:50,294
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thanks for calling.</b></i></font>

964
00:38:53,706 --> 00:38:54,832
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're in.</b></i></font>

965
00:38:59,754 --> 00:39:00,755
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, my God.
It happened.</b></i></font>

966
00:39:08,513 --> 00:39:10,186
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm going to go
get us some champagne.</b></i></font>

967
00:39:10,974 --> 00:39:12,271
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you so much.</b></i></font>

968
00:39:15,562 --> 00:39:17,439
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you for flying in.</b></i></font>

969
00:39:17,522 --> 00:39:20,025
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I wouldn't miss this
for the world.</b></i></font>

970
00:39:31,786 --> 00:39:32,878
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Hey.</b></i></font>

971
00:39:33,580 --> 00:39:36,083
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You said you had to go to the
bathroom a half hour ago.</b></i></font>

972
00:39:36,165 --> 00:39:38,213
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But you never came back
for your champagne.</b></i></font>

973
00:39:39,127 --> 00:39:40,299
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know.</b></i></font>

974
00:39:41,296 --> 00:39:42,673
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, what's wrong?</b></i></font>

975
00:39:43,298 --> 00:39:44,971
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You never asked me
how it went with Tara</b></i></font>

976
00:39:45,049 --> 00:39:46,392
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and telling her
about Mike.</b></i></font>

977
00:39:46,467 --> 00:39:47,935
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm so sorry.</b></i></font>

978
00:39:48,553 --> 00:39:51,181
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just got caught up
with the hearing.</b></i></font>

979
00:39:51,264 --> 00:39:53,358
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The thing is, I...</b></i></font>

980
00:39:53,433 --> 00:39:54,685
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I told her.</b></i></font>

981
00:39:55,101 --> 00:39:57,103
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We got into
a huge fight.</b></i></font>

982
00:39:57,186 --> 00:39:58,813
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And she said she
needed to think about</b></i></font>

983
00:39:58,897 --> 00:40:00,444
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>whether or not she
could forgive me.</b></i></font>

984
00:40:00,523 --> 00:40:01,570
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And?</b></i></font>

985
00:40:01,649 --> 00:40:04,089
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She just called when Harvey was
giving us the news about Mike.</b></i></font>

986
00:40:04,152 --> 00:40:06,154
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Left a 15-second
voicemail.</b></i></font>

987
00:40:06,279 --> 00:40:07,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm afraid
to listen to it.</b></i></font>

988
00:40:07,947 --> 00:40:08,948
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis.</b></i></font>

989
00:40:09,032 --> 00:40:10,152
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>She's either
going to tell me</b></i></font>

990
00:40:10,158 --> 00:40:11,580
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that she never wants
to see me again</b></i></font>

991
00:40:11,659 --> 00:40:13,457
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>or that she wants
to make up.</b></i></font>

992
00:40:13,536 --> 00:40:15,789
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Do you want me
to listen for you?</b></i></font>

993
00:40:15,872 --> 00:40:16,919
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No.</b></i></font>

994
00:40:16,998 --> 00:40:19,376
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'd like it if you
stay with me while I do.</b></i></font>

995
00:40:19,959 --> 00:40:21,302
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Of course.</b></i></font>

996
00:40:25,673 --> 00:40:26,765
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay.</b></i></font>

997
00:41:21,854 --> 00:41:22,901
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's that?</b></i></font>

998
00:41:22,981 --> 00:41:24,181
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I wanted to
give you a present.</b></i></font>

999
00:41:24,899 --> 00:41:26,526
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Your first year's
salary in advance.</b></i></font>

1000
00:41:26,609 --> 00:41:27,735
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Welcome back.</b></i></font>

1001
00:41:27,819 --> 00:41:29,366
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I'm running
out of ways to tell you</b></i></font>

1002
00:41:29,445 --> 00:41:30,788
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't want to be
a corporate lawyer.</b></i></font>

1003
00:41:30,863 --> 00:41:32,991
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Before you answer, you might want
to take a look at this check.</b></i></font>

1004
00:41:33,074 --> 00:41:34,121
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You trying to bribe me?</b></i></font>

1005
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:35,417
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm trying to close you.</b></i></font>

1006
00:41:35,493 --> 00:41:36,494
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I told you.</b></i></font>

1007
00:41:36,577 --> 00:41:38,830
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, I get it.
You want to do good.</b></i></font>

1008
00:41:38,913 --> 00:41:40,005
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, do you
really want to do good?</b></i></font>

1009
00:41:40,081 --> 00:41:41,833
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donate half of this
to the clinic.</b></i></font>

1010
00:41:41,916 --> 00:41:43,088
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You'll fund
the place for a year.</b></i></font>

1011
00:41:43,167 --> 00:41:44,419
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, so that's what
you think I'm all about.</b></i></font>

1012
00:41:44,502 --> 00:41:45,503
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Just giving money.</b></i></font>

1013
00:41:45,586 --> 00:41:47,964
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, but I think you're about more
than just working at that place.</b></i></font>

1014
00:41:48,047 --> 00:41:49,299
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you know it.</b></i></font>

1015
00:41:49,382 --> 00:41:50,429
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you
talking about?</b></i></font>

1016
00:41:50,508 --> 00:41:51,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm offering you a deal.</b></i></font>

1017
00:41:51,843 --> 00:41:54,312
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>One for you,
one for me.</b></i></font>

1018
00:41:54,387 --> 00:41:57,357
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You can save the spotted owls,
stop global warming,</b></i></font>

1019
00:41:57,432 --> 00:42:00,106
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and help as many damsels
in distress as you'd like.</b></i></font>

1020
00:42:00,184 --> 00:42:02,812
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And the good news is you'll
be doing it from here.</b></i></font>

1021
00:42:02,895 --> 00:42:04,488
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What makes you think
I'd take you up on that?</b></i></font>

1022
00:42:04,564 --> 00:42:05,861
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because here's
the thing, Mike.</b></i></font>

1023
00:42:05,940 --> 00:42:08,034
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You want to be here
and you know it.</b></i></font>

1024
00:42:08,109 --> 00:42:09,326
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's not true.
Uh-uh.</b></i></font>

1025
00:42:09,444 --> 00:42:12,163
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I saw the look on your face
when you strong-armed Palmer</b></i></font>

1026
00:42:12,238 --> 00:42:15,492
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and you took on Seidel and
every other talented attorney</b></i></font>

1027
00:42:15,575 --> 00:42:17,418
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you've beaten
over the years.</b></i></font>

1028
00:42:17,493 --> 00:42:18,619
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I've told you
this once before.</b></i></font>

1029
00:42:18,703 --> 00:42:20,080
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This is
the major leagues.</b></i></font>

1030
00:42:20,163 --> 00:42:21,460
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't get this
feeling anywhere else.</b></i></font>

1031
00:42:21,539 --> 00:42:24,167
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm offering you
the best of both.</b></i></font>

1032
00:42:34,510 --> 00:42:35,887
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why are you giving
me a peace sign?</b></i></font>

1033
00:42:35,970 --> 00:42:37,563
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Double it.
What?</b></i></font>

1034
00:42:37,638 --> 00:42:40,812
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't want to just fund the clinic
for a year. I want to fund it for two.</b></i></font>

1035
00:42:40,892 --> 00:42:41,939
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And while we're at it,</b></i></font>

1036
00:42:42,018 --> 00:42:44,737
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want some leftover for a little
something nice for me and the wife-to-be.</b></i></font>

1037
00:42:44,812 --> 00:42:46,155
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's all it's
going to take.</b></i></font>

1038
00:42:46,230 --> 00:42:47,402
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, not even close.</b></i></font>

1039
00:42:47,482 --> 00:42:48,779
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I wouldn't have it
any other way.</b></i></font>

1040
00:42:48,858 --> 00:42:50,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Any case I want to bring
the clinic onto, I can.</b></i></font>

1041
00:42:50,902 --> 00:42:51,949
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Done.</b></i></font>

1042
00:42:52,028 --> 00:42:54,076
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Anyone I want to bring over
from the clinic, I can.</b></i></font>

1043
00:42:54,155 --> 00:42:58,080
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis doesn't get a say, you don't
get a say, no Harvard rule.</b></i></font>

1044
00:42:58,367 --> 00:42:59,459
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Done.</b></i></font>

1045
00:42:59,535 --> 00:43:00,661
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And there's
one more thing,</b></i></font>

1046
00:43:00,745 --> 00:43:02,543
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and you are not
going to like it.</b></i></font>

1047
00:43:03,414 --> 00:43:04,586
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You are not
getting my office.</b></i></font>

1048
00:43:04,665 --> 00:43:06,417
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, yes, I am.
And I will tell you why.</b></i></font>

1049
00:43:06,501 --> 00:43:07,753
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why?</b></i></font>

1050
00:43:07,835 --> 00:43:09,052
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because she's gone, Harvey.</b></i></font>

1051
00:43:10,046 --> 00:43:11,673
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And she's not
coming back.</b></i></font>

1052
00:43:13,716 --> 00:43:16,185
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's time for you
to take the reins.</b></i></font>

